{"tid":2263143,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] [有圖] sip左張咔落去依條gap度，可以點拎返出黎？","createTime":"2020-10-29T15:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T20:03:56.000Z","uid":244066,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c5c5bddeb0cf96f027840a61afa79e25b18e1be9","tid":2263143,"uid":244066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QLjxJup.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQLjxJup.png&h=ac6809c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n麻煩位：<br />\n．枱同佢左右既牆係痴死左，郁唔到張枱<br />\n．枱背有一塊連落地下既板（啡色斜線）<br />\n．因為枱同背面牆既gap應該唔夠1cm，但枱面高80cm，連肉眼都睇唔到張卡既位置，只知道大約位置<br />\n．張咔既咔脊唔係朝天，所以唔可以吊一枝水平既柱落去勾張佢卡返張咔上黎<br />\n．唔想破壞張咔／枱<br />\n<br />\n想問下有冇巴絲打諗到可以用咩工具拎返張卡？"},{"pid":"e6371052f05720831ebe4571960296c48dc55315","tid":2263143,"uid":174942,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:42:30.000Z","msg":"咁都叫有圖？仆街啦你。"},{"pid":"fd2db3e5b50b04617b43bdea55fd0fc131d4cf5a","tid":2263143,"uid":27416,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:42:57.000Z","msg":"咸濕到以為係ball gap<br />\n我錯"},{"pid":"6e0d81599568b45638ee30e7db82734d6558e8ec","tid":2263143,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:43:53.000Z","msg":"卡乜質地？"},{"pid":"410c92890a0b0179e11c2d2f9289e9f47a202849","tid":2263143,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:46:05.000Z","msg":"畀錢賠返張卡"},{"pid":"8cacab9354007780e7a44a038d83b8bac00438fc","tid":2263143,"uid":244066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e0d81599568b45638ee30e7db82734d6558e8ec","tid":2263143,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:43:53.000Z","msg":"卡乜質地？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:46:29.000Z","msg":"硬畫紙質地，即係對摺左之後係企到起身個種硬度"},{"pid":"a51b970213694431ee55649e0b185e409fcbe953","tid":2263143,"uid":366281,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202